descript.purpose: Building polygons compiled from various scales and types of mapping. Each scale of mapping has different standards for collecting building polygons. Areas considered rural will have fewer buildings depicted as polygons as they appear much tinier on the source photography. However, each mapping is complete to its respective standard. The newest additions to this file are done by scanning, registering and rectifying building footprints from location certificates.

dataqual.complete: The building coverage was created from 3 scales of mapping. Each scale of mapping has different standards for collecting building polygons. Areas considered rural will have fewer buildings depicted as polygons as they appear much tinier on the source photography. However, each mapping is complete to its respective standard. Each scale of mapping has a different vintage and may be very dated and seem incomplete for todays purpose.
